<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="155" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1437,896,1138]" pageId="18" pageNumber="155">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,328,1076,1102]" pageId="18" pageNumber="155">Etymology</emphasis>
. The genus name is based on the Greek noun 
<emphasis box="[841,928,1076,1102]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="155">dokidos</emphasis>
= small beam or rod, a reference to the shape of the sclerites in the polyp body and tentacles.
</paragraph>
